M|examples|Your personal library of proven techniques, patterns, and tools
M|examples|is at `~/.claude/skills/`.
M|examples|Browse categories: `ls ~/.claude/skills/`
M|examples|Search: `grep -r "keyword" ~/.claude/skills/ --include="SKILL.md"`
